DISCIPLINES
Ventrue: Dominate (Dominar), Fortitude (Fortitude), Presence (Presença).
Toreador: Auspex (Auspício), Celerity (Celeridade), Presence (Presença).
Tremere: Auspex (Auspício), Blood Sorcery (Feitiçaria de Sangue), Dominate (Dominar).
Malkavian: Auspex (Auspício), Dominate (Dominar), Obfuscate (Ofuscação).
Nosferatu: Animalism (Animalismo), Obfuscate (Ofuscação), Potence (Potência).
Banu Haqim: Blood Sorcery (Feitiçaria de Sangue), Celerity (Celeridade), Obfuscate (Ofuscação).
Lasombra: Dominate (Dominar), Oblivion (Oblívio), Potence (Potência).
Brujah: Celerity (Celeridade), Potence (Potência), Presence (Presença).
Gangrel: Animalism (Animalismo), Fortitude (Fortitude), Protean (Metamorfose).
The Ministry: Obfuscate (Ofuscação), Presence (Presença), Protean (Metamorfose).
Ravnos: Animalism (Animalismo), Obfuscate (Ofuscação), Presence (Presença).
Hecata: Auspex (Auspício), Fortitude (Fortitude), Oblivion (Oblívio).
Tzimisce: Animalism (Animalismo), Dominate (Dominar), Protean (Metamorfose).
Salubri: Auspex (Auspício), Dominate (Dominar), Fortitude (Fortitude).

NIVELS
1. Animalism
Feral Whispers: Communicate with animals.
Beckoning: Call specific types of animals to you.
Quell the Beast: Calm the hunger/rage in others or yourself.
Subsume the Spirit: Possess the body of an animal.
Drawing Out the Beast: Project your frenzy onto someone else.
Animal Succulence: Gain more nourishment from animal blood.
Conquer the Beast: Total mastery over your own frenzy.
Taunt the Caged Beast: Force others into frenzy from a distance.
Unleash the Hellish Horde: Control thousands of animals simultaneously.

2. Auspex
Heightened Senses: Sharpen all five physical senses.
Aura Perception: See the colors of a soul and emotions.
The Spirit's Touch: Read psychic impressions from objects.
Telepathy: Read and project thoughts.
Psychic Projection: Leave the body in astral form.
Prediction/Clairvoyance: See the immediate future or distant places.
Mirror Reflex: React to attacks before they happen.
Psychic Assault: Mental attack that causes physical brain damage.
False Slumber: Project your consciousness while in Torpor.

3. Celerity
Levels 1-5: Passive increase in speed and extra actions per turn.
Level 6 (Projectile): Throw objects with lethal, supersonic force.
Level 7 (Flower of Death): Strike everyone in an area in a split second.
Level 8 (Zephyr): Run across water or up vertical walls.
Level 9 (Between the Ticks): Move so fast that time appears to stop.

4. Dominate
Command: A single-word command.
Mesmerize: Deep hypnotic suggestions.
The Forgetful Mind: Rewrite or erase memories.
Conditioning: Long-term mental brainwashing.
Possession: Take full control of a mortal’s body.
Obedience: Command via touch without eye contact.
Mass Manipulation: Dominate entire crowds at once.
Far Mastery: Dominate anyone you know, anywhere in the world.
Speak Through the Blood: Command all your biological descendants at once.

5. Fortitude
Levels 1-5: Supernatural toughness and damage soaking.
Level 6 (Personal Armor): Anyone striking the vampire takes damage themselves.
Level 7 (Shared Strength): Grant your invulnerability to allies.
Level 8 (Adamantine): Virtually immune to all non-magical weapons.
Level 9 (King of the Mountain): Cannot be moved or knocked down by any force.

6. Obfuscate
Silence of Death: Perfect silence in a small radius.
Unseen Presence: Invisibility while remaining still.
Mask of a Thousand Faces: Change your physical appearance.
Vanish from the Mind's Eye: Disappear while being watched.
Cloak the Gathered: Hide a group of people with you.
Conceal: Hide massive objects like buildings or cars.
Cache: Leave someone invisible even after you leave.
Old Friend: People perceive you as someone they love/trust.
Create Name: Create a identity so perfect that history rewrites itself to include it.

7. Presence
Awe: Attract everyone's attention and admiration.
Dread Gaze: Paralyze a victim with supernatural fear.
Entrancement: Make someone your emotional slave.
Summon: Force someone to travel to your location.
Majesty: No one can find the will to attack or insult you.
Love: The victim feels eternal, unconditional love for you.
Cooperation: Force an entire group to work in perfect harmony.
Ironclad Command: Your Presence cannot be resisted by spending Willpower.
Pulse of the City: Control the emotional "vibe" and mood of an entire city.

8. Potence
Levels 1-5: Passive supernatural strength.
Level 6 (Fist of Caine): Punch the air to strike someone yards away.
Level 7 (Earthshock): Slam the ground to create a localized earthquake.
Level 8 (Flick): Kill a mortal or launch a vampire with just a finger flick.
Level 9 (Might of Heroes): Lift mountains, skyscrapers, or ships.

9. Protean
Eyes of the Beast: See in total darkness.
Feral Claws: Grow claws that cause Aggravated Damage.
Earth Meld: Sink into the ground for safety.
Shape of the Beast: Turn into a wolf or bat.
Mist Form: Turn into an intangible cloud of mist.
Earth Control: Move through the earth as if it were water.
Restore the Mortal Visage: Temporarily regain a beautiful human form.
Purify the Impure: Instantly expel stakes, poisons, or silver from the body.
Inviolate Form: Your body becomes immutable; nothing can transform or permanently harm your physical shape.

1. Blood Sorcery (Thaumaturgy)
In classic lore, this discipline is mastered through Paths and Rituals. This progression follows the most common one, the Path of Blood:
Level 1 — A Taste for Blood: Discern the generation and remaining blood of another vampire by tasting their vitae.
Level 2 — Blood Rage: Force a target to spend their blood pool against their will (e.g., forcing a physical buff or a heal).
Level 3 — Blood of Potency: Temporarily lower your own generation, increasing your power for a short time.
Level 4 — Theft of Vitriol: Physically pull blood out of a victim's body from a distance, drawing it directly into the sorcerer.
Level 5 — Cauldron of Blood: Boil a victim’s blood inside their own veins, causing massive lethal or aggravated damage.
Level 6 — Mastery of Blood: Gain total control over the blood of anyone the sorcerer has ever tasted.
Level 7 — Blood Curse: Place a permanent curse on an entire lineage or turn a target's blood into water.
Level 8 — Blood of the Ancestors: The caster can access the blood and memories of any vampire in their direct lineage.
Level 9 — Utter Destruction: Instantly turn all the blood within a target's body into ash, ending them immediately.

2. Oblivion (Obtenebration)
This represents the Lasombra clan's absolute mastery over the shadows of the Abyss:
Level 1 — Shadow Play: Basic manipulation of ambient shadows to distort light and intimidate.
Level 2 — Shroud of Night: Create a cloud of supernatural darkness that smothers all light and sound.
Level 3 — Arms of the Abyss: Summon semi-solid shadow tentacles that can grapple and strike foes.
Level 4 — Black Metamorphosis: The vampire is shrouded in living shadow armor, gaining extra reach and terrifying power.
Level 5 — Tenebrous Form: The vampire transforms into a fluid, two-dimensional shadow, becoming immune to physical harm.
Level 6 — The Darkness Within: Project a shadow that drains the life force and soul of anyone it touches.
Level 7 — Shadowstep: Step into one shadow and instantly emerge from another miles away.
Level 8 — Entombment: Trap a victim in a pocket dimension within the Abyss, leaving them in eternal sensory deprivation.
Level 9 — Tenebrous Avatar: The vampire becomes a massive, city-sized entity of pure shadow, capable of consuming entire neighborhoods.

